sentences: She began her career as concert violinist, working internationally until 1990.
She produced and presented for the BBC Radio 3 before leading the development of new work for English National Opera between 1998 and 2001.

In 2001 she moved to the USA to direct the International Festival of Arts and Ideas in Connecticut, returning to Europe in 2005 as CEO and Artistic Director of the Stavanger2008, European Capital of Culture 2008.
